# USC CSCI531 HW1

## Compile

type `make hw1` to generate executable.
type `make clean` to clear up *.o file and executable.

## Command

### hexdump: ./hw1 hexdump filename
if filename is not specified, stdin will be used as input source.

### base64 encode: ./hw1 enc-base64 filename
if filename is not specified, stdin will be used as input source.

### base64 decode: ./hw1 dec-base64 filename
if filename is not specified, stdin will be used as input source.
